  "finalSubmissionGuidelines": "<h3><span><span><span><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\">Final Submission Guidelines</span></strong></span></span></span></h3>\n\n<div class=\"ng-binding\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 254);\">\n<h2><span><span><span><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\">Submission Deliverables</span></strong></span></span></span></h2>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span>A complete list of deliverables can be viewed in the TopCoder Assembly Competition Tutorial at:<a href=\"http://apps.topcoder.com/wiki/display/tc/Assembly+Competition+Tutorials\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(255, 138, 0); border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; -webkit-transition: 0.3s; transition: 0.3s; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; word-wrap: break-word; background: 0px 0px;\">http://apps.topcoder.com/wiki/display/tc/Assembly+Competition+Tutorials&nbsp;</a></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>Below is an overview of the deliverables:</span></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span>Working Unity3D 5.0+ app (including source code) that covers all requirements.</span></li>\n\t<li><span>A complete and detailed deployment document explaining how to deploy and verify the application including configuration information.</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2><span><span><span><span style=\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>Final Submission</strong></span></span></span></span></h2>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span>For each member, the final submission should be uploaded via the challenge detail page on&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(255, 138, 0); border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; -webkit-transition: 0.3s; transition: 0.3s; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; word-wrap: break-word; background: 0px 0px;\">topcoder.com</a></span></span></span></span></p>\n</div>\n",
